    "body" : "<pre><code>arrayList.toArray(new Custom[0]);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html#toArray%28java.lang.Object%5B%5D%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://download.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html#toArray%28java.lang.Object[]%29</a></p>\n"
