  "title" : "make arrayList.toArray() return more specific types",
  "body" : "<p>So, normally <code>ArrayList.toArray()</code> would return a type of <code>Object[]</code>....but supposed it's an \n<code>Arraylist</code> of object <code>Custom</code>, how do I make <code>toArray()</code> to return a type of <code>Custom[]</code> rather than <code>Object[]</code>?</p>\n"
